                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300114-75-off413 t18300114-75-crimeloc416"></join>. On the evening of the 19th of December I saw the prisoner take these shoes off a chair in the shop - he was going out: I went, and took them from him - he had come in to buy a pair of shoes, and my shopman showed him some; he said he did it from distress.</p>
